{"tid":1388542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警對英文單字「Five」與 「Fire」有嚴重聽障","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:44.000Z","uid":281029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27fcc02c8efd8c6f37d57f7f2b9e07ac58c6dae4","tid":1388542,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"有警察的塲合，有一個英文單字<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「Five」</span></span>是不能隨便發聲。<br />\n英文水評有限<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「Five」與「Fire」</span></span>英文發音他們來說是一種障礙。<br />\n警察對香港人已陷入自大、仇視、瘋狂、獸性，用英文發音「Five」與「Fire」要謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUys5Oc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUys5Oc.png&h=11bbe5a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10cb7d165bb7548261853b7470683f39d1a1c286","tid":1388542,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=164941b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=4664f178\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"}]}